      "stars": 4,
      "lesson": {
        "title": {
          "fr": "Leçon : Context Managers - Gestion Automatique des Ressources",
          "en": "Lesson: Context Managers - Automatic Resource Management",
          "es": "Lección: Context Managers - Gestión Automática de Recursos",
          "de": "Lektion: Kontextmanager - Automatische Ressourcenverwaltung"
        },
        "content": {
          "fr": "Les context managers en Python sont comme des gardiens magiques qui gèrent automatiquement l'ouverture et la fermeture des ressources !\n\n**Concepts clés :**\n- **Context Manager** : Objet qui gère l'entrée et la sortie d'un contexte\n- **with statement** : Syntaxe pour utiliser les context managers\n- **Ressource** : Fichier, connexion base de données, lock, etc.\n- **Cleanup automatique** : Libération garantie des ressources\n\n**Syntaxe with :**\n```python\nwith open(\"fichier.txt\", \"r\") as f:\n    contenu = f.read()\n# f est automatiquement fermé ici\n```\n\n**Créer son propre context manager :**\n```python\nclass MonContextManager:\n    def __enter__(self):\n        print(\"Entrée dans le contexte\")\n        return self\n    \n    def __exit__(self, exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb):\n        print(\"Sortie du contexte\")\n        return False\n\nwith MonContextManager() as cm:\n    print(\"À l'intérieur du contexte\")\n```\n\nPrêt à devenir le gardien des ressources ?",
          "en": "Context managers in Python are like magical guardians that automatically manage the opening and closing of resources!\n\n**Key concepts:**\n- **Context Manager**: Object that manages entry and exit of a context\n- **with statement**: Syntax to use context managers\n- **Resource**: File, database connection, lock, etc.\n- **Automatic cleanup**: Guaranteed resource release\n\n**with syntax:**\n```python\nwith open(\"file.txt\", \"r\") as f:\n    content = f.read()\n# f is automatically closed here\n```\n\n**Creating your own context manager:**\n```python\nclass MyContextManager:\n    def __enter__(self):\n        print(\"Entering context\")\n        return self\n    \n    def __exit__(self, exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb):\n        print(\"Exiting context\")\n        return False\n\nwith MyContextManager() as cm:\n    print(\"Inside context\")\n```\n\nReady to become the guardian of resources?",
          "es": "Los context managers en Python son como guardianes mágicos que gestionan automáticamente la apertura y cierre de recursos!\n\n**Conceptos clave:**\n- **Context Manager**: Objeto que gestiona la entrada y salida de un contexto\n- **with statement**: Sintaxis para usar context managers\n- **Recurso**: Archivo, conexión base de datos, lock, etc.\n- **Limpieza automática**: Liberación garantizada de recursos\n\n**Sintaxis with:**\n```python\nwith open(\"archivo.txt\", \"r\") as f:\n    contenido = f.read()\n# f se cierra automáticamente aquí\n```\n\n**Crear tu propio context manager:**\n```python\nclass MiContextManager:\n    def __enter__(self):\n        print(\"Entrando al contexto\")\n        return self\n    \n    def __exit__(self, exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb):\n        print(\"Saliendo del contexto\")\n        return False\n\nwith MiContextManager() as cm:\n    print(\"Dentro del contexto\")\n```\n\n¿Listo para convertirte en el guardián de recursos?",
          "de": "Kontextmanager in Python sind wie magische Wächter, die automatisch das Öffnen und Schließen von Ressourcen verwalten!\n\n**Wichtige Konzepte:**\n- **Kontextmanager**: Objekt, das Ein- und Austritt eines Kontexts verwaltet\n- **with Anweisung**: Syntax zur Verwendung von Kontextmanagern\n- **Ressource**: Datei, Datenbankverbindung, Lock, etc.\n- **Automatische Bereinigung**: Garantierte Ressourcenfreigabe\n\n**with Syntax:**\n```python\nwith open(\"datei.txt\", \"r\") as f:\n    inhalt = f.read()\n# f wird automatisch hier geschlossen\n```\n\n**Eigener Kontextmanager erstellen:**\n```python\nclass MeinKontextManager:\n    def __enter__(self):\n        print(\"Kontext betreten\")\n        return self\n    \n    def __exit__(self, exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb):\n        print(\"Kontext verlassen\")\n        return False\n\nwith MeinKontextManager() as cm:\n    print(\"Innerhalb des Kontexts\")\n```\n\nBereit, der Wächter der Ressourcen zu werden?"
        },
